property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'CreateCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "CustomerInvoice"."ID"       AS "ID",
    "CustomerInvoice"."ID"                                          AS "CustomerInvoice",
    "CustomerInvoice"."CreationTime"                                AS "Time",
    "CustomerInvoice"."CreatedBy_ID"                                AS "ExecutedBy",
    "CustomerInvoice"."CreationExecutionType"                       AS "ExecutionType",
    "CustomerInvoice"."CustomerInvoiceType"                         AS "CustomerInvoiceType"
FROM "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"
WHERE "CustomerInvoice"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'CreateCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "CustomerInvoice"."ID"      AS "ID",
	"CustomerInvoiceLine__DeliveryLines"."DeliveryLines_ID"        AS "DeliveryLine"
FROM "r_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine__DeliveryLines" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine__DeliveryLines"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine__DeliveryLines"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID" = "CustomerInvoice"."ID"
WHERE "CustomerInvoice"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine__DeliveryLines"."DeliveryLines_ID" IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
    'CreateCustomerInvoice' || '::' || "CustomerInvoice"."ID"                          AS "ID",
	"CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"."SalesOrderScheduleLines_ID"        AS "SalesOrderScheduleLine"
FROM "r_o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoiceLine" AS "CustomerInvoiceLine"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."ID" = "CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_CustomerInvoice" AS "CustomerInvoice"
        ON "CustomerInvoiceLine"."CustomerInvoice_ID" = "CustomerInvoice"."ID"
WHERE "CustomerInvoice"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
    AND "CustomerInvoiceLine__SalesOrderScheduleLines"."SalesOrderScheduleLines_ID" IS NOT NULL
